description.en: Fracture Labs is a team of veteran game developers who are creating an open world survival game with a blockchain based economy, called DECIMATED. The team is creating a 64km2 map in Unreal Engine 4, where players can choose to play a human citizen or a cyborg cop, and must compete with each other to earn cryptocurrency (DIO) in a massive persistent online world.
